snippet.title: FAR CRY 5 X MONDO  Edition - Meet artist Jay Shaw and discover his collaboration with Ubisoft
snippet.description:
FAR CRY 5 x Mondo Edition, featuring a set of artwork inspired by the captivating universe of the game, is now available for pre-order exclusively on the Ubisoft Store : http://ubi.li/wf44h
Meet Jay Shaw the Creative Director of Mondo, a collective of artists famous for their unique take movie poster art, discussing his collaboration with Ubisoft to create the Far Cry 5 x Mondo Limited Edition.
